snippet.title: Serena Williams Reacts To Meghan Markle's Oprah Interview
snippet.description:
As people react to Meghan Markle for falsely saying her and Harry actually got married before their televised wedding, Roz Weston, Graeme O'Neil and guest co-host Wanna Thompson react to Serena Williams showing her support during ET Canada Live.
